<p>Concretely, this means guests are welcome at Christ the Reconciler. Come and visit, whether for an hour, a day, an Open Table, a retreat, or an extended stay.  We have a beautiful guest room, the George & Hanna Miley Suite, that is always set aside for visitors.  If you would like to come, please contact us.  You can also see the calendar for our schedule of Open Tables and Retreats.  We look forward to seeing you!</p>